Okay, what about my first question? How would two smaller guilds booking the planes work? I mean, if each one can book a day, that's two days they've occuppied in the schedule, even though neither guild can handle a plane alone. What are you saving with the 18 rule if it can be bypassed this way?<br>
<br>
The above's not argument, it's questions. I'm asking questions. I'm hoping for answers. It's ridiculous that I have to emphasize this; sometimes a cigar is just a cigar.<br>
<br>
Aldrin Moonwalker<br>
